<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīya vibhuya sālivāhana
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śakavarṣaṁgaḷu 1304 Ahaṁthā sa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rvadhārisaṁvachara mārgaśira śu 7 budhavā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ra <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> śrīmanmahārājādhirāja rājapara
<lb n="5" break="no"/><unclear>mēśvara</unclear> vīrapratāpa hiriyadēvarāyamahā
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> bāri Anumaṁtadēvarige dūpa
<lb n="7"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> Aṁgaraṁgavayibhōgake kadiri nāra
<lb n="8"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> vadake dhāreneradu koṭa grāma madhuko
<lb n="9"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> vāḍi A dēvara sīmehāḷanu dhāreyera<unclear>du</unclear> ne
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> dēvarige sarvamānya yī dharmmakke Ā 
<lb n="11"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> tapidare taṁde tāya vānarāsili koṁda
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Ivaru yī dharmake tapidare poḍavuṭidaṁ
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ge tapidaru <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> Avarige suṁkama sahā
<lb n="14"/>sarvamānyavāgi pālisideU
<lb n="15"/>śrīvirupākṣa <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

